      "body" : "Is the order of deletion relevant? If not, something like this is both easier to read and likely more efficient:\r\n```\r\nfor x in self.p2ps:\r\n    if x.connection is not None:\r\n        x.connection.disconnect_node()\r\nself.p2ps = []\r\n```",
